      <title>特朗普的 FBI 人选卡什·帕特尔曾起诉过所谓的对手</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/fbi-pick-kash-patel-has-a-history-of-suing-perceived-adversaries</link>
      <description><![CDATA[多年来，卡什·帕特尔一直将自己认为的对手告上法庭。如今，他被候任总统唐纳德·特朗普选中领导联邦调查局，批评者担心他会利用该局的庞大资源进行报复。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/fbi-pick-kash-patel-has-a-history-of-suing-perceived-adversaries</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 17:07:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯塔默任命彼得·曼德尔森为英国驻美国大使</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/starmer-names-peter-mandelson-as-uk-ambassador-to-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[基尔·斯塔默已确认，他将任命贸易专家、工党资深人士彼得·曼德尔森 (Peter Mandelson) 为英国下一任驻华盛顿大使。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/starmer-names-peter-mandelson-as-uk-ambassador-to-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 16:44:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新民主党领袖辛格表示将投票推翻特鲁多政府</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/ex-trudeau-ally-jagmeet-singh-says-he-ll-vote-to-bring-government-down</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大一名反对党领袖表示，他的党团计划投票反对贾斯汀·特鲁多的政府，除非总理寻求暂时中止议会，否则此举将导致该国于明年初陷入选举。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/ex-trudeau-ally-jagmeet-singh-says-he-ll-vote-to-bring-government-down</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 16:40:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管誓言废除奴隶制，斯塔默仍将盟友和工会老板置于上议院</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/starmer-puts-allies-union-bosses-in-lords-despite-abolition-vow</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 任命了 30 名新工党贵族，以寻求解决上议院的政治不平衡问题，尽管他在选举中承诺要精简并最终更换上议院。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/starmer-puts-allies-union-bosses-in-lords-despite-abolition-vow</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 16:02:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普承诺结束俄罗斯战争为何让乌克兰感到担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/why-ukraine-is-worried-about-trump-s-promise-to-end-russia-s-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普表示，他将迅速通过谈判结束俄罗斯在乌克兰的战争。这让北约盟友们担心，他是否会撤回美国对基辅政府的支持，并迫使基辅政府接受俄罗斯永久占领乌克兰领土。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/why-ukraine-is-worried-about-trump-s-promise-to-end-russia-s-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 15:58:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特鲁多与弗里兰的惊人通话引发加拿大政治危机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/the-call-with-chrystia-freeland-that-threw-justin-trudeau-government-into-crisis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贾斯汀·特鲁多的政治前途几个月来一直不稳定。但威胁到他加拿大总理职位的事件在几天之内就演变成一场危机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/the-call-with-chrystia-freeland-that-threw-justin-trudeau-government-into-crisis</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 15:39:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拉马福萨签署南非备受争议的教育法案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/ramaphosa-signs-s-africa-s-controversial-bela-act-fully-into-law</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非总统西里尔·拉马福萨表示，一项威胁该国新执政联盟分裂的有争议的教育法案将得到全面实施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/ramaphosa-signs-s-africa-s-controversial-bela-act-fully-into-law</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 15:22:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克威胁关闭政府，众议院共和党领导人已准备好拨款计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/house-may-vote-on-temporary-fix-to-stop-shutdown-networks-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[众议院议长迈克·约翰逊周五上午与他的副手和民主党人制定了战略，如何在美国政府午夜关门期限之前迅速在众议院通过一项支出法案。此前，当选总统唐纳德·特朗普支持的一项法案于周四失败。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/house-may-vote-on-temporary-fix-to-stop-shutdown-networks-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 13:37:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普将价值 40 亿美元的媒体公司股份转入儿子管理的信托基金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/trump-moves-4-billion-trump-media-stake-into-trust-run-by-son</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普将其持有的媒体公司价值约 40 亿美元的股份转让给由其长子小唐纳德·特朗普控制的信托基金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/trump-moves-4-billion-trump-media-stake-into-trust-run-by-son</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 12:48:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢拉削减开支计划获国会最终批准</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/brazil-congress-further-dilutes-lula-s-spending-cut-package</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经过一周的深夜投票，巴西参议院批准了削弱版的政府支出削减方案，旨在缓解投资者对该国财政状况恶化的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/brazil-congress-further-dilutes-lula-s-spending-cut-package</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 20:50:28 GMT</pubDate>
